task.summary: fixed bug in new added preferences
noted down bugs and new features

added support for accounts and budget ordered alphabetically by name fixed but account / budget dropdown view showing wrong colors added past budget period stats in the budgets list view remove unused import refactoring budget getPercentage method added basic support for account stats (work in progress) added support to import / export settings added support for percentage text over circular shapes
added budgets stats fixes on accounts stats fixed balance label on budget screen
removed 'DaySingleValues' as day list option since same as 'Day'
completed custom order for account and budget
fix account/budget order not saved if never re-ordered
updated project reference and dependencies support for feee on transfer transaction material design look and feel added analytics package (work in progress)
